<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8367713>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12 Muccanella cundalinensis gen.et sp.nov., (A–D, F–H) male holotype; female allotype (E).(A, B) thoracopod VIII (posterior view); (C, D) thoracopod VIII (frontal view); (E) thoracopod VIII female allotype (frontal view); (F) first pleopod; (G) furcal ramus and dorsal seta (dorsal view); (H) uropod (dorsal view). Scale bar in mm. Abbreviations:O.lb, outer lobe; Bsp, basipod; Endp,. endopod Exp, exopod P.pr, posterior projection; Fr.pr, frontal projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8367713/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

